data.title: The Barn: Traditional Country Music Station
data.meta_description: Tune in to Ashland County's Country - The Barn for the best classic and traditional country music in the area. Join us for a taste of true country music!
data.text:
We play traditional country music old and new. Classic country from George Jones, Merle Haggard, Dolly Parton just to name a few.

Miss the 1990's?

George Strait, Alan Jackson, Patty Loveless and all your favorites from 90's are here on The Barn

Not all of todays country artists make bad music, we highlight some new Artists keepin' it country every hour!
